Rajat Gupta Action by SEC ‘Bizarre,’ U.S. Judge Tells Lawyers

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   H u r t a d o
-- 
2011-03-16T16:53:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/sec-decision-not-to-sue-gupta-bizarre-judge-in-related-case-tells-court.html
The decision by the U.S. Securities
and Exchange Commission to file an administrative action against
former  Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS)  director Rajat K. Gupta and not
sue him is “bizarre,” a federal judge in a Galleon Group LLC 
case said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
